OL,3,CEx-church warden's murder conviction
OL,4,Cto be reviewed again by appeal judges
OL,6,FThe murder conviction of a former
OL,7,Fchurch warden for killing a university
OL,8,Flecturer following a campaign of
OL,9,Fphysical and mental torture is to be
OL,10,Freferred to the Court of Appeal.
OL,12,FBenjamin Field, 34, is serving a life
OL,13,Fsentence for the murder of Peter
OL,14,FFarquhar, 69, after a jury accepted
OL,15,Fthat he had driven the pensioner to
OL,16,Fthink he was losing his mind in order
OL,17,Fto inherit his house and money.
