OL,3,CEx-church warden's murder conviction
OL,4,Cto be reviewed again by appeal judges
OL,6,FThe prosecution case at trial was that
OL,7,FField secretly gave Mr Farquhar
OL,8,Ftranquiliser drugs and spiked his
OL,9,Fwhisky, hoping that his eventual death
OL,10,Fwould look like suicide or an accident.
OL,12,FField, of Wellingborough Road, Olney,
OL,13,FBuckinghamshire, was ordered to serve
OL,14,Fat least 36 years behind bars in
OL,15,FOctober 2019 after being convicted of
OL,16,FMr Farquhar's murder following a trial
OL,17,Fat Oxford Crown Court.
