OL,3,CEx-church warden's murder conviction
OL,4,Cto be reviewed again by appeal judges
OL,6,FOn Tuesday, legal review body the
OL,7,FCriminal Cases Review Commission
OL,8,F(CCRC) said it would refer the case to
OL,9,Fthe Court of Appeal over a legal
OL,10,Fargument linked to whether Mr Farquhar
OL,11,Fhad been tricked into drinking the
OL,12,Fwhisky or had done so willingly.
OL,14,FField previously attempted to appeal
OL,15,Fagainst his conviction but this was
OL,16,Frejected by the Court of Appeal in
OL,17,F2021. He was denied permission to
OL,18,Freopen the appeal in March the
OL,19,Ffollowing year.
