OL,3,CEx-church warden's murder conviction
OL,4,Cto be reviewed again by appeal judges
OL,6,FHe then applied to the CCRC to
OL,7,Fconsider his case in September 2022.
OL,9,FField's crime came to light after he
OL,10,Fbegan targeting Mr Farquhar's
OL,11,Fneighbour, Ann Moore-Martin, in the
OL,12,Fvillage of Maids Moreton,
OL,13,FBuckinghamshire.
OL,15,FThe sexually promiscuous Field also
OL,16,Fmanipulated Miss Moore-Martin, a
OL,17,Fdeeply religious retired headteacher,
OL,18,Fby writing messages on her mirrors
OL,19,Fpurporting to be from God.
