OL,3,CEx-church warden's murder conviction
OL,4,Cto be reviewed again by appeal judges
OL,6,FHe admitted fraudulently being in
OL,7,Frelationships with the pensioners as
OL,8,Fpart of his plan to get them to change
OL,9,Ftheir wills.
OL,11,FMr Farquhar, who was torn about his
OL,12,Fsexuality because of his religion,
OL,13,Fdied in October 2015 while Miss Moore-
OL,14,FMartin died in May 2017 from natural
OL,15,Fcauses.
OL,17,FField underwent a "betrothal" ceremony
OL,18,Fwith gay Mr Farquhar while also having
OL,19,Fa string of girlfriends and a
OL,20,Frelationship with Miss Moore-Martin.
